OL,3,CFormer MP pleads guilty to gambling on
OL,4,Celection date
OL,6,FA close aide to former prime minister
OL,7,FRishi Sunak has pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fcheating at gambling with bets on the
OL,9,Fdate of the 2024 general election.
OL,11,FCraig Williams, 41, who was the
OL,12,FConservative MP for Montgomeryshire
OL,13,Fand Cardiff North, admitted using
OL,14,Fconfidential information to place bets
OL,15,Fon the timing of the poll.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
