FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782771508
OL,3,CFormer MP pleads guilty to gambling on
OL,4,Celection date
OL,6,FHe was part of Mr Sunak's inner
OL,7,Fcircle, having been appointed to be
OL,8,Fthe former prime minister's
OL,9,Fparliamentary private secretary, and
OL,10,Fhe attended a series of planning
OL,11,Fmeetings in Downing Street ahead of
OL,12,Fthe 2024 election.
OL,14,FWilliams, of Llanfair Caereinion,
OL,15,FWelshpool, Powys, entered his guilty
OL,16,Fplea at a hearing at Southwark Crown
OL,17,FCourt on Monday (29 June).
OL,19,FHe bet #250, #100, and #22.50 on the
OL,20,Felection date, prosecutors said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782771508
OL,3,CFormer MP pleads guilty to gambling on
OL,4,Celection date
OL,6,FWhen the scandal first broke, Williams
OL,7,Fadmitted making a "huge error of
OL,8,Fjudgment" when confronted over a #100
OL,9,Fbet.
OL,11,FAt Monday's court hearing, Amy Hind,
OL,12,F35, the wife of Conservative deputy
OL,13,Fdigital director Anthony Hind, also
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to cheating on the date
OL,15,Fof the election while 13 other co-
OL,16,Fdefendants pleaded not guilty to
OL,17,Fcheating at gambling in relation to
OL,18,Fbets on the 2024 election.
