FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782771508
OL,3,CFormer MP pleads guilty to gambling on
OL,4,Celection date
OL,6,FWilliams was first the MP for Cardiff
OL,7,FNorth between 2015 and 2017 before he
OL,8,Flost his seat to Labour MP Anna
OL,9,FMcMorrin.
OL,11,FHe was then elected MP for
OL,12,FMontgomeryshire at the 2019 general
OL,13,Felection, and lost his seat at the
OL,14,F2024 election in the wake of the
OL,15,Fbetting scandal, and as the
OL,16,FConservatives faced electoral wipeout
OL,17,Facross the UK.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
