FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782771508
OL,3,CFormer MP pleads guilty to gambling on
OL,4,Celection date
OL,6,FProsecutor Zoe Johnson KC said three
OL,7,Ffurther cheating charges, which
OL,8,FWilliams denies, will be dropped when
OL,9,Fhe is sentenced.
OL,11,FShe said Williams, a member of the
OL,12,FPrivy Council, was "given a privileged
OL,13,Fposition, he was party to a number of
OL,14,Fmeetings in both Downing Street and
OL,15,FConservative headquarters when the
OL,16,Fdate of the general election was
OL,17,Fdiscussed".
OL,26,@tD@TOUyD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/12
