OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782771508
OL,3,CFormer MP pleads guilty to gambling on
OL,4,Celection date
OL,6,F"He has now accepted by his plea that
OL,7,Fhe used highly sensitive and
OL,8,Fconfidential information to place bets
OL,9,Fand to profit," she said.
OL,11,FAmy Hind, 35, the wife of Conservative
OL,12,Fdeputy digital director Anthony Hind,
OL,13,Falso pleaded guilty to cheating on the
OL,14,Fdate of the election.
OL,16,FShe had placed bets of #10, #5, and
OL,17,F#20 on the date of the election,
OL,18,Fbefore on May 13 2024 attempting to
OL,19,Fstake #767 and #700 on a July poll.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@OO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782771508
OL,3,CFormer MP pleads guilty to gambling on
OL,4,Celection date
OL,6,FThose attempts failed, the court
OL,7,Fheard, and she attempted to place a
OL,8,F#700 bet the following day before
OL,9,Fsuccessfully placing a #100 bet on a
OL,10,FJuly election, at odds of 11-1.
OL,12,FA separate charge against her husband,
OL,13,F37, that he had cheated at gambling by
OL,14,Fpassing information to his wife was
OL,15,Fthen dropped by prosecutors.
OL,17,FHind is due to be sentenced by Judge
OL,18,FTony Baumgartner, the Recorder of
OL,19,FWestminster, on October 23.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
