FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782771508
OL,3,CFormer MP pleads guilty to gambling on
OL,4,Celection date
OL,6,FWilliams will not be sentenced until
OL,7,Fco-defendants have stood trial.
OL,9,FAlso at the hearing on Monday, 13 co-
OL,10,Fdefendants pleaded not guilty to
OL,11,Fcheating at gambling in relation to
OL,12,Fbets on the 2024 election.
OL,14,FThe criminal charges were brought by
OL,15,Fthe Gambling Commission after
OL,16,FOperation Scott was launched to
OL,17,Finvestigate gambling by politicians
OL,18,Fand employees of the Conservative
OL,19,FParty in the lead-up to the 2024
OL,20,Fgeneral election.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
