PN,43209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782771508
OL,3,CFormer MP pleads guilty to gambling on
OL,4,Celection date
OL,6,FAmong those to deny the charges are
OL,7,FRussell George, 52, who was a member
OL,8,Fof the Senedd for Montgomeryshire, and
OL,9,FThomas James, 39, who was the director
OL,10,Fof the Welsh Conservatives.
OL,12,FAlso charged is Jeremy Hunt, 56, who
OL,13,Fwas a close protection officer at the
OL,14,FMet and part of the police team
OL,15,Fworking in Downing Street.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
