CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782771508
OL,3,CFormer MP pleads guilty to gambling on
OL,4,Celection date
OL,6,FCo-defendants are Anthony Lee, 49, a
OL,7,FConservative Party director of
OL,8,Fcampaigning, and his wife, Laura
OL,9,FSaunders, 38, who was head of
OL,10,Finternational at Tory HQ and the
OL,11,Fparliamentary candidate for Bristol
OL,12,FNorth-West.
OL,14,FLee faces two charges, alleging he
OL,15,Fplaced bets himself and passed
OL,16,Fconfidential information to his wife
OL,17,Fto allegedly help her to cheat at
OL,18,Fgambling.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
