OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782771508
OL,3,CFormer MP pleads guilty to gambling on
OL,4,Celection date
OL,6,FAlso accused are Tory Party officials
OL,7,FNick Mason, 52, the chief data
OL,8,Fofficer, Iain Makepeace, 48, head of
OL,9,Fdesign and print, his boss, Simon
OL,10,FChatfield, 52, who was chief marketing
OL,11,Fofficer, and deputy director of
OL,12,Finsights James Ward, 41.
OL,14,FCo-defendants are also Paul Place, 55,
OL,15,Fa consultant employed by the
OL,16,FConservative Party, political
OL,17,Fstrategist and former parliamentary
OL,18,Fcandidate Charlotte Lang, 37, and
OL,19,FJacob Willmer, 40, the brother of
OL,20,FConservative Party deputy chief of
OL,21,Fstaff Toby Willmer.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/12
